\sum_{j,k\geq 0}\frac{(j+k)a^{j+k}}{j!k!}=2ae^{2a} = \sum_{l=0}^\infty \frac{l(2a)^l}{l!}.
j,k
j+k = m
\begin{align} \sum_{j,k \geqslant 0} \frac{(j+k)a^{j+k}}{j!k!} &= \sum_{m=0}^\infty \left(\sum_{k=0}^m \frac{1}{k!(m-k)!}\right)ma^m\\ &=\sum_{m=0}^\infty \left(\sum_{k=0}^m \binom{m}{k}\right)\frac{ma^m}{m!}\\ &= \sum_{m=0}^\infty \frac{m2^ma^m}{m!} \end{align}
